# Sosnovka, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Sosnovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Selenginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 26 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Sosnovka is located 68&nbsp;km southwest of Gusinoozyorsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Shana is the nearest rural locality.
